parameters:
Man: I've lent Pole about 10 million G. It's all debt he racked up from
gambling.

Man: Well, if he can't pay it back, maybe I'll take something he cherishes most.
Hehe...

\C[24][Becky]\C[0] Beat, is it you guys again? My husband is seriously injured. If you're here to
collect the debt, please wait until he's healed.

Man: Shut up. Your husband is an irresponsible man even when he's not injured.
You know what happens if he can't pay the debt, right? Hehe...

Man: If you understand, then that's good. You don't want to be driven out of the
village, do you? Heheheh
Hehe... I need Becky, can you call her for me?

We're the guys who lent a large sum of money to Pole. We're keeping watch to
make sure he doesn't run away. Seems like he's injured, but we still need to get
back what he owes us.

\C[29][Noah]\C[0] "Luna, I won't run away. I'm sure my leg will heal, so please believe in me and
wait."
\I[89]HINT: To select each H event, talk to "Noah during the day".
\C[29][Noah]\C[0] To get excited seeing Luna being sold off... Have I gone mad...?
\I[89]HINT: To select each H event, talk to "Noah during the day".

\C[20][Noah]\C[0] Ugh... I can't believe the village chief's relative, a debt collector, has come
all the way here. I can't work anymore, what should I do? I have nothing left to
give.

\C[20][Noah]\C[0] Ugh... If I don't pay back my debts, they're going to kill me... I want to
work, but my body just won't move the way I want it to...
